model.productcontainer

Class ProductContainer

  • java.lang.Object
    • model.common.Model
      • model.productcontainer.ProductContainer
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, IModel
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ProductGroup, StorageUnit

    public class ProductContainer
extends Model
    The ProductContainer is the base class for ProductGroup and for StorageUnit. It defines the shared interface for these objects.
